OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780575067
OL,3,CUK Athletics fined #350,000 for
OL,4,CParalympian's 'avoidable' death
OL,6,FUK Athletics Ltd has been fined
OL,7,F#350,000 over the "wholly avoidable"
OL,8,Fdeath of a Paralympian killed when a
OL,9,Fpractice cage collapsed on his head.
OL,11,FFather-of-five Abdullah Hayayei, 36,
OL,12,Fwas preparing to represent the United
OL,13,FArab Emirates at the World Athletics
OL,14,FChampionships in London when the 440lb
OL,15,Fmetal structure fell on him at Newham
OL,16,FLeisure Centre in east London on July
OL,17,F11, 2017.
OL,26,@oD@SOUoD@dO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780575067
OL,3,CUK Athletics fined #350,000 for
OL,4,CParalympian's 'avoidable' death
OL,6,FThe 5ft high cage toppled over because
OL,7,Fit was put up incorrectly and without
OL,8,Fits base plate, in an "accident
OL,9,Fwaiting to happen".
OL,11,FUK Athletics Ltd pleaded guilty to
OL,12,Fcorporate manslaughter and on Tuesday
OL,13,Fwas fined #350,000 plus #44,000 costs,
OL,14,Fto be paid over six years.
OL,16,FKeith Davies, 79, who was head of
OL,17,Fsport for the 2017 World Paralympic
OL,18,FAthletics Championships, admitted a
OL,19,Fhealth and safety charge and was
OL,20,Fhanded a community order of 175 hours
OL,21,Fof unpaid work.
OL,26,@pD@WOUqD@RO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780575067
OL,3,CUK Athletics fined #350,000 for
OL,4,CParalympian's 'avoidable' death
OL,6,FSentencing, Judge Richard Marks KC
OL,7,Fsaid the death of Mr Hayayei was
OL,8,F"tragic, untimely and wholly
OL,9,Favoidable".
OL,11,FThe judge noted failings by UK
OL,12,FAthletics were not a "one off" but
OL,13,Fsaid any financial penalty would
OL,14,F"weaken" its ability to support
OL,15,Findividual athletes and athletics in
OL,16,Fthe community.
OL,18,FHe told retired PE teacher Davies that
OL,19,Fhe knew, or ought to have known, base
OL,20,Fplates were an "integral part" of the
OL,21,Fcage construction.
OL,26,@pD@AOUqD@JO]tD@VOUtD@^O]vD@AOUvD@HO]|D@
OL,26,APOU|D@^O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780575067
OL,3,CUK Athletics fined #350,000 for
OL,4,CParalympian's 'avoidable' death
OL,6,FFollowing an earlier collapse of an
OL,7,Fidentical cage, he was "on notice",
OL,8,Fand the judge said: "This was an
OL,9,Faccident which sooner or later was
OL,10,Fwaiting to happen."
OL,12,FPreviously, Mr Hayayei's widow,
OL,13,FBadriah, who attended court by
OL,14,Fvideolink from the UAE, described the
OL,15,Fimpact his death has had on herself
OL,16,Fand her five children, who were aged
OL,17,Fbetween two and 14 when they lost
OL,18,Ftheir father.
OL,26,@oD@XOUoD@bO]pD@UOUrD@SO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780575067
OL,3,CUK Athletics fined #350,000 for
OL,4,CParalympian's 'avoidable' death
OL,6,F"I hope the court looks at the
OL,7,Fmagnitude of the harm to our family
OL,8,Fbecause Abdullah was not just a person
OL,9,Fwho passed away. He was a father, a
OL,10,Fhusband with responsibilities, dreams
OL,11,Fand a future," she said.
OL,13,F"I hope the court takes a just stance
OL,14,Fagainst everyone who caused this
OL,15,Fbecause what happened was not just a
OL,16,Fsimple mistake but the result of
OL,17,Fnegligence, gross negligence, that
OL,18,Fcould have been avoided if safety
OL,19,Fprocedures adhered to.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780575067
OL,3,CUK Athletics fined #350,000 for
OL,4,CParalympian's 'avoidable' death
OL,6,F"My husband went out to represent his
OL,7,Fcountry and raise the name of the UAE
OL,8,Fbut he returned as a corpse because of
OL,9,Fthis negligence."
OL,11,FThe court heard wheelchair user Mr
OL,12,FHayayei, who had cerebral palsy, had
OL,13,Fbeen due to compete in the para
OL,14,Fathletics shot-put event during the
OL,15,FWorld Athletics Championships in
OL,16,FStratford.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@QO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780575067
OL,3,CUK Athletics fined #350,000 for
OL,4,CParalympian's 'avoidable' death
OL,6,FIn the five years since UK Athletics
OL,7,Facquired two identical cages
OL,8,Foriginally used in the 2012 Olympics,
OL,9,Fthey had never been properly assembled
OL,10,Fwith the base plates attached, the
OL,11,Fcourt heard.
OL,13,FThe two practice cages had been given
OL,14,Fto UK Athletics by the organisation
OL,15,Fcommittee for the London 2012 Games.
OL,17,FOne of them had collapsed in 2012
OL,18,Falthough no-one was injured on that
OL,19,Foccasion, the court was told.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780575067
OL,3,CUK Athletics fined #350,000 for
OL,4,CParalympian's 'avoidable' death
OL,6,FProsecutor John Price KC said: "Over
OL,7,Fthis period, very many athletes will
OL,8,Fhave been within the cages and many
OL,9,Fmore standing or passing close by."
OL,11,FIt was a perennial hazard, or to use a
OL,12,Ffamiliar phrase, an accident waiting
OL,13,Fto happen."
OL,15,FOn the afternoon of July 11 2017, Mr
OL,16,FHayayei was training in a cage under
OL,17,Fsupervision of the UAE team coach,
OL,18,FAyman Mohamed Ali Ibrahim, and his
OL,19,Fassistant.
OL,26,@nD@`OUqD@cOUuD@KO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780575067
OL,3,CUK Athletics fined #350,000 for
OL,4,CParalympian's 'avoidable' death
OL,6,FIn a statement, Mr Ibrahim said:
OL,7,F"Whilst Abdullah was carrying out the
OL,8,Fthrows, we were surprised by the wind
OL,9,Fthat came all of a sudden and moved
OL,10,Fthe whole cage, causing the bar on the
OL,11,Ftop to fall directly on his head. My
OL,12,Fassistant and I rushed to help."
OL,14,FMr Hayayei collapsed immediately and
OL,15,Fhad to be cut free from netting and,
OL,16,Fdespite the efforts of medics, he
OL,17,Fnever regained consciousness and died
OL,18,Fat 7.20pm.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@`O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780575067
OL,3,CUK Athletics fined #350,000 for
OL,4,CParalympian's 'avoidable' death
OL,6,FDavies had claimed UK Athletics had
OL,7,Fnever been supplied with base plates,
OL,8,Fbut this proved not to be true, the
OL,9,Fcourt was told.
OL,11,FThe base plates for one of the cages
OL,12,Fhad been photographed in storage at
OL,13,Fthe London stadium but were moved
OL,14,Fafter the incident to Cambridge.
OL,16,FThose for the collapsed cage have
OL,17,Fnever been recovered despite searches.
OL,19,FIn the wake of the fatal incident, a
OL,20,Fprohibition notice was put on both the
OL,21,Fcages barring them from being used.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780575067
OL,3,CUK Athletics fined #350,000 for
OL,4,CParalympian's 'avoidable' death
OL,6,FMr Price said it was a "remarkable
OL,7,Ffeature" of the case that UK Athletics
OL,8,Ftried to get the notice lifted on the
OL,9,Fsecond cage, which was refused.
OL,11,FAccording to Sentencing Council
OL,12,Fguidelines, corporate manslaughter
OL,13,Fcarries a fine of between #180,000 and
OL,14,F#20 million.
OL,16,FUK Athletics, the national governing
OL,17,Fbody for athletics in the UK, had an
OL,18,Fannual revenue of #13.8 million with a
OL,19,F"modest profit" of #107,000, according
OL,20,Fto accounts to March 2025.
OL,26,@nD@XOUoD@HO]{D@AOU{D@OO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780575067
OL,3,CUK Athletics fined #350,000 for
OL,4,CParalympian's 'avoidable' death
OL,6,FThe organisation is expected to make a
OL,7,Floss of #400,000 in the following
OL,8,Fyear, the court heard.
OL,10,FDetective Chief Inspector Lucie Card
OL,11,Fof Scotland Yard said: "Abdullah was a
OL,12,Ftalented athlete whose life was
OL,13,Fcruelly cut short by the failings by
OL,14,Fthose who were meant to keep him safe.
OL,16,F"The lead technician of the firm that
OL,17,Fhad manufactured the throwing cage
OL,18,Fknew within seconds of seeing the
OL,19,Fscene that the equipment hadn't been
OL,20,Ferected properly.
OL,26,@sD@XOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G12/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780575067
OL,3,CUK Athletics fined #350,000 for
OL,4,CParalympian's 'avoidable' death
OL,6,F"Our investigation demonstrated that
OL,7,Ffor years, the cage, which was donated
OL,8,Fto UK Athletics after the 2012
OL,9,FOlympics, wasn't being properly
OL,10,Fsecured by UK Athletics and its
OL,11,Frepresentatives.
OL,13,F"Establishing what failures caused
OL,14,FAbdullah's death has taken years of
OL,15,Fmeticulous work by a committed team of
OL,16,Fdetectives. It is no less than his
OL,17,Ffamily deserved."
OL,26,@uD@AOUyD@QO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G13/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40814
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780575067
OL,3,CUK Athletics fined #350,000 for
OL,4,CParalympian's 'avoidable' death
OL,6,FSpeaking outside court after the
OL,7,Fsentencing, she said: "His death arose
OL,8,Ffrom negligent approaches to health
OL,9,Fand safety, and a failure to construct
OL,10,Fthe throwing cage with the necessary
OL,11,Fsupportive equipment. This was a
OL,12,Ftragedy waiting to happen."
OL,14,FShe added: "We reviewed more than
OL,15,F1,500 documents, took 160 witness
OL,16,Fstatements, and brought experts in to
OL,17,Fbetter understand and evidence issues
OL,18,Ffrom corporate governance to the
OL,19,Fdesign of the throwing cage.
OL,26,@oD@WOUtD@[O]vD@LOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G14/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40815
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1780575067
OL,3,CUK Athletics fined #350,000 for
OL,4,CParalympian's 'avoidable' death
OL,6,F"I would like to thank Abdullah's
OL,7,Ffamily for their support and patience
OL,8,Fas we work to secure justice for him
OL,9,Fover the course of this incredibly
OL,10,Fcomplex investigation. Today, my
OL,11,Fthoughts remain with his family and
OL,12,Fhis loved ones."
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@PO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G15/15
